Question-2 | open | Should library content be copied or linked from SG/Send?
# Option A: Copy role definitions into library repo (independent, can diverge)
# Option B: Library repo submodule or symlink pointing at SG/Send team/roles/
# Recommendation: Copy — keeps library truly independent. SG/Send role reviews
# can reference library versions. Library is the canonical source after migration.

